        {'instr':'Open the meeting recap from your Teams calendar. On the recap page, click the **Copilot** icon (top-right). Paste the prompt below.', 'prompt':'Produce confidential meeting minutes using our M&A template with sections: Confidentiality Notice, Attendees and Conflicts, Discussion Themes, Decisions Taken, Reserved Decisions for Board, Workstream Owners, Next Checkpoints. Highlight any disclosure-sensitive item in red and add a one-line confidentiality reminder at the top." Copy the structured output into a new Word document marked Strictly Confidential and save as Minutes_Potential_Merger.docx.'},
        {'instr':'Open the meeting recap from your Teams calendar. On the recap page, click the **Copilot** icon (top-right). Paste the prompt below.', 'prompt':'Format as a vendor-negotiation minute with sections: Vendor and Owner, Commercial Terms Discussed, Concessions Offered, Concessions Received, Open Items, Approval Threshold, Next Step Owner and Date. Highlight any term that requires CFO sign-off in amber, and any term that requires Operations Review Committee sign-off in red." Copy the result into a new Word document, then save as Minutes_Vendor_Negotiation.docx and forward the link to Procurement, Legal and Finance for review.'}
