        {'instr':'Open Outlook on the Web. Click **New email** and open the **Copilot pane** on the right. Paste the prompt below.', 'prompt':'Draft an internal email to the team immediately after the Board of Directors, summarising the key decisions, the expectations for Red-status areas, and the rules for external communications until approved messaging is issued. Reference the playbook and the brand documents for the disclosure restrictions. End with 3 bullet points titled "What you must do today". Use Coach my response to keep the tone firm and aligned.'}
